{"id":640558,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/【立此存照】404哀悼日的中国网站是黑白的-但/","date":"2020-04-04T08:44:39Z","modified":"2020-04-04T08:45:05Z","title":"【立此存照】“404哀悼日”的中国网站是黑白的 但他们是彩色的","content":"<p>4月4日，庚子年清明节，中国举行全国范围内的新冠肺炎哀悼活动，深切悼念“抗击新冠肺炎疫情斗争牺牲烈士和逝世同胞”。</p>\n<p>自2020年4月4日00:00:00起，几乎全部的中国境内大型商业网站及政府网站都变成了黑白色。此举动疑似来自于网信部门对国务院全国哀悼日活动的统一部署。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640564\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"829\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n-163x300.jpg 163w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n-556x1024.jpg 556w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n-768x1415.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1125807657_15858737649811n-834x1536.jpg 834w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>4月4日，搜狐、B站、腾讯、京东等大型网站均将首页调为了<strong>纯黑白页面：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640571\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899-300x164.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899-1024x560.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/4a1d89f8-5818-4c88-af8e-2266b8cdb899-768x420.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640573\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d-300x164.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d-1024x560.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/f6046172-3f0d-47d7-97d1-c3faf4118f8d-768x420.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640572\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5-300x164.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5-1024x560.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/ceb0d419-0220-42fe-8350-cf34b8c101e5-768x420.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640574\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_.png 1575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-300x151.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-1024x515.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-768x386.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-1536x772.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-1080x543.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/jd.com_-1280x640.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>4月3日，“全国哀悼日”前一天，许多游戏公司发布了停服公告：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640565\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器.jpg 917w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器-300x229.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器-768x586.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器2-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640566\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器2-1.jpg 893w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器2-1-300x277.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/游戏服务器2-1-768x710.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>截至4月3日晚22点，有超过20万个微博账号更换灰色头像。（来源：新浪科技）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640567\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"511\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af.png 1132w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af-294x300.png 294w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af-1003x1024.png 1003w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af-768x784.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af-1080x1103.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/5cca49c70e430aefede1089dc34c22af-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>然而，却有网友发现，在“404哀悼日”当天，中国外交部网站及中国政府网，却将网站整体黑白处理后，唯独将习近平等领导人的照片彩色显示。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640563\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部.png 1250w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-114x300.png 114w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-390x1024.png 390w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-768x2015.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-586x1536.png 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-781x2048.png 781w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/中华人民共和国外交部-1080x2833.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1d8609c9-9e3d-4055-ae4c-917858aadeee.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-640575\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1d8609c9-9e3d-4055-ae4c-917858aadeee.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1d8609c9-9e3d-4055-ae4c-917858aadeee.jpeg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1d8609c9-9e3d-4055-ae4c-917858aadeee-300x286.jpeg 300w, https://chi